em\">DROP POINT FIXED BLADE KNIFE: Drop point blade design offers a strong, durable tip that is ideal for controlled cutting and precision tasks; suitable to include with general outdoor gear, hunting gear, survival kits, camping essentials and more</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">440 STAINLESS STEEL BLADE: Features excellent edge retention and corrosion resistance, making the drop point fixed blade knife suitable for a variety of cutting and other tasks in different environments; blade measures 2.75 inches in length</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">FRICTION SHEATH: Rather than relying on a locking mechanism or snap closure, this utility knife comes with a friction sheath, purposefully designed to mold around the blade, ensuring a snug and secure fit at all times; handle also feature small hole for lanyard if desired (not included)</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">FINGER HOLE SPIN BEARINGS: Allowing for enhanced grip, control and effortless spinning action; Unique integrated spin bearings within the finger hole provide fluid rotation, making it perfect for tactical use or stylish knife flipping tricks</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">SPECIFICATIONS: Dimensions: 7.5 x 1.5 x 0.5 inches; Weight: 0.22lbs; Color: Brown</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t</tbody>\n\t\t\t\t</table>\n\t\t\t</div><!-- /product-specs -->\n\t\t</div>\n\t\t<div class=\"col-md-6\">\n\t\t\t<h1>ASR Outdoor 7.5 Inch Drop Point Fixed Blade Knife with Finger Hole with Spin Bearings and Sheath, Brown</h1>\n\t\t\t<h2>MSRP <span class=\"msrp-strike\">19.99</span></h2>\n\t\t\t<p>Whether out in the wild, for EDC or including with a survival kit or bug out bag, this lightweight fixed blade drop point knife features a strong, durable tip that is ideal for controlled cutting and precision tasks; that being said, the knife with sheath also makes a great all around utility knife to include with general outdoor gear, hunting gear, camping essentials and more.</p><p>Designed for ergonomic excellence, the handle incorporates a unique built in finger hole with integrated spin bearings, allowing for smooth rotation and effortless handling. Whether you're enhancing your knife skills or need a secure grip for tough jobs, this innovative design delivers both function and finesse.</p><p>Featuring a sharp, 440 stainless steel blade that is rust resistant and offers excellent edge retention and sharpness, this knife excels in slicing and utility tasks, making it a reliable companion for both outdoor adventures and tactical situations alike. The pocket knife also comes with a built in hole for a lanyard if desired (not included). And lastly, fitted with a custom molded plastic friction sheath, this drop point fixed blade knife offers secure retention and quick access when you need it most.</p><p>Blade Length: 2.75 inches</p><p>Overall Length: 7.5 inches</p>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"d-flex d-flex-col grid-60 center text-center bg-grey\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"newsletter-header m-all-1rem all-caps\">Newsletter</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"grid-100\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>SUBSCRIBE for Early Access to Sales</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>Up to 90% Off</p>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"grid-80 center\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<a class=\"newsletter-link\" href=\"https://my.ebay.com/ws/eBayISAPI.dll?AcceptSavedSeller&amp;sellerid=dealsonlywebstore\" target=\"_blank\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"newsletter-btn all-caps\">Sign Up</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div><!-- /col-md-6 -->\n\t\t<div class=\"col-md-12 footer\">\n\t\t\t<p>© 2025</p></div></div>",
